<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>7835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：从前，有一个很可爱的小女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：她总是带着一顶小红帽，所以每个人都叫她“小红帽”。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：多么美好的一天！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：你好，小鸟儿！早上好，松鼠先生！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：有一天，小红帽的妈妈带给了她一个坏消息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈：你的奶奶生病了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈：我给她做了一些食物，但是我不能给她送过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：可怜的奶奶。我给她送过去，妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈：真是好女儿！这是食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈：过森林的时候小心点儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：我会的。再见，妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：奶奶住在森林的另一边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：小红帽拿着篮子，向奶奶的家走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：森林里住着一只又大又坏又饥饿的大灰狼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：森林里没有什么吃的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：我吃够了松鼠。兔子尝起来像发了霉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：我想吃点儿新鲜美味的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：就在那时，小红帽走了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：她看到大灰狼的时候停下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：噢，你好，大灰狼先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116074</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：她看起来很美味。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122077</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：你好啊，小女孩儿。你要去哪儿？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：我要去奶奶家。她生病了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：对陌生人讲话，尤其是饥饿的陌生人，是很危险的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：但是，小红帽并不知道这一点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：真可怜。你奶奶住在哪里？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：也许我也可以去拜访她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：她住在森林的另一边。很容易就能找到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：快点儿走吧，不能让奶奶等太久。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：小红帽继续赶路。大灰狼看着她离开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：然后他想出了一个计划。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：我要跑到奶奶的房子，然后在那里等。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：等她过来了……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：大灰狼穿过森林，跑到奶奶家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：你好？有人在吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：没有回答。房子里空无一人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：奶奶去哪儿了？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：就在那时，小红帽向房子走过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：大灰狼披上了奶奶的披巾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：然后跳上了床。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：咚咚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：是谁啊？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：是我，小红帽啊，奶奶。我给您带了一些食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：噢，真是好孩子。进来吧，宝贝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：奶奶，您的声音怎么了？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：是流感。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：但是奶奶，您的胳膊好粗啊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：那是为了更好地拥抱你，宝贝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：奶奶，您的耳朵真大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：那是为了更好地听你的声音，宝贝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：奶奶，您的眼睛真大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：那是为了更清楚地看你，宝贝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：奶奶，您的牙齿真大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：那是为了吃你，宝贝！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：可怜的小红帽！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：救命！救命啊！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：没人可以帮你。你现在是我的了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：大灰狼用他粗壮的胳膊抓住了小红帽，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：他张开血盆大口，准备用锋利的牙齿咬下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：正在那时……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奶奶：发生什么事了？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：我要吃掉你的孙女。一定很好吃！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奶奶：我正想做些汤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奶奶：让我先放进去一些蔬菜，然后你再把她放进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：奶奶！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：别担心。奶奶并不是真的让大灰狼吃掉小红帽。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>346271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>349966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：奶奶也有一个计划。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>349967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：快点儿！我很饿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>353890</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>358928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奶奶：等一下！我就快好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>358929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>367635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：奶奶把辣椒放进了锅里。她用木头汤勺搅拌着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>367636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>374617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奶奶：嗯！尝尝这个，狼先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>374618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>378639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：啊！好辣！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>378640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>384998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奶奶：哎呀！尝尝这个吧。你会感觉好一点的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>384999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>389004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：啊！好辣！啊！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>389005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>392410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奶奶：噢！喝点水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>392411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>400676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大灰狼：啊！救命！我要赶快离开这里！啊！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>400677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>405902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：大灰狼的嘴巴、舌头和嗓子都像在燃烧，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>405903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>410393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：于是他飞快地跑出了奶奶的房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>410394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>413635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：他们再也没有见过他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>413636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>418508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奶奶：小红帽，你得到了什么教训？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>418509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>424089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：奶奶，我再也不跟陌生人说话了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>424090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>429613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小红帽：还有，我再也不敢喝奶奶做的汤了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>429614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>434627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁白：结束。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
